Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I got divorced three years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No. More accurately,\Nmy wife ran away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Because instead of listening to her...\NI mostly listened to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife told me that I was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"just a collector of people's\Ninnermost thoughts..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I peer into the deep abyss harbored in\Nthe depths of peoples' hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a chance I may sink\Ninto that deep abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fourth victim was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,an 18-year-old woman\Nfrom Munich, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you experience\Nany sexual pleasure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,0:00:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,when you butchered her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.31,0:01:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside, ask me\Nabout my 12th killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.89,0:01:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Hanna Kemp\Nfrom Krupp-Haus...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.12,0:01:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She was 52, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.26,0:01:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time...I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.46,0:01:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.33,0:01:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to talk about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll probably ask you about it\Nsooner or later,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.63,0:01:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but right now, I want to hear about\Nthe 11 killings before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I ask you,\Nwhen you commit a murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,when do you reach\Nthe peak of your sexual pleasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Before or after?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As discussed, the victims were\Nall long-haired girls
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,between the ages of\N16 and 18 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,These cases definitely fall\Nin the realm of sexual homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But he has also confessed\Nto his 12th murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The victim in this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kemp, is not only older\Nthan his other victims, at 52,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but does not appear to have\Nsexual scarring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he claims to have carried out\Nthe killing for a friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,it appears that he is trying to\Ndisrupt the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. This was the only way\NI could visit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know my reason, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that I'm a serial killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have newspapers, television,\Nand rumors from college friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did you come to me\Nof all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't that close...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you despised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought that you despised\Nme whenever our eyes met...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah ha... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it money?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you were an authority\Non criminal psychology...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something I want you to\Ntake a look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"Look at me! Look at me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"See how big the monster inside\Nof me has grown, Dr. Tenma!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Help me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"The monster inside of me\Nis about to explode!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. This Johan is the one\Nwho really killed the director
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and went on to kill the foster parents\Nwho took care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He disappeared once more\Nleaving messages like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to find him\Nas soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have to prove your\Ninnocence as soon as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nearly 20 years ago, there was a man\Nwho had been at the top of his class
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,at a famous medical university...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, a Japanese student\Ntransferred to his school,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and that man's position changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The student was sociable
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and quickly earned\Neveryone's respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore,\Nhe got excellent grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who was always\Nat the top of the class
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,easily slipped down\Nafter the first semester test.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,During the second semester test...\Nthe man became desperate
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to take back his place\Nat the top of the class...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He did perfectly in all of his subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The final test was on\Nforensic medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,a subject that the man\Nstruggled with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All his work would be for nothing\Nif he failed this test...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He used his last resort...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I can be at the top of the class!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Japanese man\Nnever told anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, the man\Nreturned to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So is there anything you can tell me\Nabout these two messages?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he have what you would call\Na split personality?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to say\Nthat one personality
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is committing the crimes\Nand the other is trying to stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, there are examples\Nof serial murderers
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving messages like these\Nat crime scenes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But, sometimes, they can be a means\Nto escape their crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Telling the difference is\Nthe job of a psychoanalyst!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people think that serial\Nmurderers are introverted,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's a big misconception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some who are intelligent,\Nsociable, and good conversationalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They are skilled liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:08:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he just playing with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good to jump to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me\Na little more about Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I became divorced three years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, more accurately,\Nmy wife ran away from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you, Rudy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was very interesting, Tenma.\NI'd like to research this thoroughly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give me a call in two weeks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can relate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What can you relate to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster...he talks about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a monster, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, there is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a monster within you,\Nwithin him, and even within me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's armchair theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:09:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that monsters\Nexist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate being looked down on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Warden...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There are scarier things in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure he's going to come to you,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you as soon as he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:09:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I want him as a research subject\Nafter you arrest him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma is\Na very interesting criminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll tell you something interesting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Mrs. Kemp's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the underground storeroom.\NYou'll understand if you go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's proof that monsters do exist...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'd like to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... All right...\NThen, I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sergeant Kohl?\NI promised to meet Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,8 PM at the Oder Park,\Nin front of the fountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I am verifying\NJurgens route on the day of his crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.34,0:11:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,According to his confession,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,he broke into this storeroom\Nand spent several hours here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When Mrs. Kemp returned home,\Nhe forced his way into
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the second-floor bedroom\Nand committed his crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing out of the ordinary...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many picture frames...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kemp is shown...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A doll, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything abnormal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no proof of the monster\Nthat Jurgens spoke of!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought, the 12th murder was\Ndone to disrupt the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He confessed that he committed\Nthe crime as a favor for a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,By calling that friend a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I was a child, I was\Ndisciplined by my mother daily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was a big doll\Nthat my mom cherished...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a long haired...girl doll...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I asked that doll for help\Nas I was being hit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it only looked at me and grinned...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that storehouse was filled\Nwith pictures of my mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wherever I looked, there was\NMom... Mom... Mom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was watching me all this time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exactly as he described...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Jurgens change this storehouse\Nto be like the one from his childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Jurgens when he was a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He shouldn't have any connection\Nwith Mrs. Kemp when he was a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Jurgens' childhood face is pasted on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This one too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one... And this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kemp never had any children...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's proof that monsters do exist...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...just did as I was told\Nin a letter from my friend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}F-Friend?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day...I received a white envelope\Nwithout a return or mailing address.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At first, I was annoyed\Nby his familiarity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said that he understood me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The letters came every day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He loved to write letters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But before I knew it,\NI could hardly wait for his letters...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I enjoyed them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought...that he might\Nreally be a friend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then one day, I was called out\Nby those letters{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to go to the storehouse\Nof a certain home...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was it Mrs. Kemp's storehouse?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder how he knows...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder how he knows\Nabout my childhood...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was confused\Nat Mrs. Kemp's house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"What's the meaning of this?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Mrs. Kemp is...my mom?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before I realized it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had gone to the second floor\Nand killed Mrs. Kemp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He loves to write letters!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That friend also sent letters\Nto Mrs. Kemp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Look at me! Look at me!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"See how big the monster inside\Nof me has grown, Dr. Tenma!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Help me!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The monster inside of me\Nis about to explode!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the message that Johan left!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The friend... Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...actually exists?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already far past eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sergeant Kohl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's come...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The longhaired Asian...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you\Nwhen you're busy, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I analyzed what you said.\NI thought that you made it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think that Johan existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he was an imaginary person\Nyou made up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha–?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rudy, listen to me! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, I'm researching\Na serial murderer named Jurgens...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one case that's different\Nfrom his usual crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget that, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finished for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The carnival is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell everyone to apprehend him\Nwhen I give the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fail to catch\NDr. Tenma's conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma...\NYou despised me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You despised me ever since\Nyou saw me cheating in college...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sergeant Kohl, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Gillen and Tenma are headed\Ntoward the west exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll get lost among\Nthe leaving carnival crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, I probably\Nshould be despised...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rudy, forget about that, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, I hid a cheat sheet\Nright here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:18:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Run away you're surrounded\Nby the police.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look! Let's walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the doctor being threatened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's too much noise around,\Nso I can't hear them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,– Wait...\N– Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jurgens said that he killed\NMrs. Kemp for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something from\Nthe basement of Mrs. Kemp's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kemp never had any children...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Johan and Jurgens' friend\Nare probably the same person!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They've passed through the west exit.\NShall I apprehend him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Tenma may be carrying a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a letter\Nwith the same message as Johan's
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in Mrs. Kemp's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan lived off Mrs. Kemp\Nand disposed of her
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,when he no longer had a use for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As you said, he might have done it\Nto erase his past...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't talk specifically at this point,\Nbut I'll tell you what I've figured out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how,\Nbut Johan can smell out murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He can pry into their loneliness\Nand control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There haven't been any murders\Nof any foster parents
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.05,0:20:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that Johan was taking advantage of\Nduring his young adulthood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.18,0:20:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's probably because,\Nage-wise,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,he no longer needed foster parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's another possibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan finally found\Nhis ideal family and joined them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would he try to\Nerase his past?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he have some sort of reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,For what purpose could he have\Njoined this family?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We've arrived at the bus terminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirm what bus he's getting on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Get cars to the terminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to track him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought you a bus ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma...there's a way to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,turn yourself in now\Nand prove your innocence!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.04,0:21:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...not chasing Johan\Nto prove my innocence!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that\Nyou're going to kill Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!\NI never despised you...really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were an interesting guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.53,0:21:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but I never had the chance\Nto talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But now we've finally become friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:22:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But...when I cheated back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.77,0:22:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked in my direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I also cheated back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.41,0:22:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.92,0:22:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The five buses left at\Nabout the same time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma...
